{"word":"ἀμφιφῶν","slug":"ἀμφιφῶν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6133\" key=\"a)mfifw=n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀμφιφῶν</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ῶντος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, properly <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood> of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀμφιφάω,</foreign> cake offered to Munychian Artemis <sense id=\"n6133.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by double light,</tr_> i.e. either <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">surrounded by lighted tapers,</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">offered when sun and moon were both visible,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0486.tlg001:156\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pherecr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">156</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0487.tlg001:67\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philem.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">67</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:6:75\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.75</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:94:55\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">94.55</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}